text: Welcome back and congratulations on finishing Module 1. We're now going to begin Module 2, the proficiency. In Module 2 we're going to focus on some core principles and a lot of practical examples and then most importantly we're going to finally start developing some key volume profiling strategies. Good luck and I hope you enjoy Module 2.
